name: Deep Dive History
description: In-depth, highly researched documentaries and narratives on specific historical events, cultures, or failed technologies.

name: Hyper-Niche Gaming Lore
description: Content dedicated to the deep, complex storylines, characters, and history of a single, popular video game universe.

name: Productivity & Efficiency
description: Guides, tutorials, and templates for maximizing personal and digital efficiency, often featuring tools like Notion and Trello.

name: Ambient/Focus Media
description: Content designed for passive consumption, relaxation, study, or sleep using soundscapes and looping visuals.

name: Digital Finance Hacks
description: Actionable, short-form educational content focused on personal finance, crypto, budgeting, and investment strategies.

name: Cottagecore/Aesthetic DIY
description: Visually aesthetic, satisfying hand-cam content focusing on detailed crafts, miniature creation, and domestic arts.

name: True Crime & Mystery
description: Narrative-driven content exploring unsolved cases, historical conspiracies, and psychological thrillers.

name: AI & Automation
description: Niches focusing on leveraging artificial intelligence, machine learning, and automation for business or personal growth.
